00:04:31.250 --> 00:04:33.799
that, that's my, my main question. Of course, there

73
00:04:33.799 --> 00:04:37.459
is this experience of reality that changes, but there's

74
00:04:37.459 --> 00:04:40.720
a base to a certain internal logic. It's, it's

75
00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:43.799
people being challenged to severe, in a, in a,

76
00:04:43.880 --> 00:04:48.290
in a very severe degree that creates such um

77
00:04:48.359 --> 00:04:51.079
a mindset, so to speak. And that challenge can

