00:11:13.429 --> 00:11:18.549
here I'm not exclusively referring to psychosis necessarily, it

183
00:11:18.549 --> 00:11:22.659
can be any other sort of uh mental phenomenon.

184
00:11:22.830 --> 00:11:24.390
I mean, do you think that there are at

185
00:11:24.390 --> 00:11:29.820
least some instances where Uh, people might express distress,

186
00:11:29.900 --> 00:11:32.880
but it is, it is not something that really

