00:13:58.630 --> 00:14:01.239
be lazy, uh, because you don't have a job.

227
00:14:01.489 --> 00:14:02.070
So there's

228
00:14:02.070 --> 00:14:05.510
yeah, it usually comes attached to some sort of

229
00:14:05.510 --> 00:14:07.640
a more. OR character failing, right,

230
00:14:08.369 --> 00:14:11.450
and so then you have the stigmatization, but once

